						Nusq[uam] ha[e]ret Trismegisti Quodlibetum.
					</marginalia_text>
					<person name="Hermes Trismegistus"/>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				The subtlety of Trismegistus never stays fixed.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		
